好好 <br />\n解散警隊呢樣野都無乜人講<br />\n612 721 811 831 新屋嶺"},{"pid":"c1b18539ab08f9f0929b94f2916dbb602241bd13","tid":1587593,"uid":79453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0bc09430c0c4e7d8ac02bc1567038117121b425e","tid":1587593,"uid":294,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"80327a40eb6e648fdf987cc1c472af62da6b1203","tid":1587593,"uid":34810,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:59:21.000Z","msg":"曾健成都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"依家識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:32:48.000Z","msg":"以前做過立法會議員"},{"pid":"f8b739b7752e569b463f37d6e76ccadac0262aad","tid":1587593,"uid":213969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69b4ef5349a37a24fb603cd53c968b58fbf6fcb8","tid":1587593,"uid":302917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"350e633f88d05885cbd37547fd9f1f868a1e4787","tid":1587593,"uid":322732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"262e228159049187c8e539c6a3d7b0d9c3553721","tid":1587593,"uid":294,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"以前有咩威水史<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:03:30.000Z","msg":"曾加入民主黨，是民主黨的創黨成員之一，並於1995年的立法局議員選舉中，以曾任地盤判頭的身份代表新九組中的「漁農、礦產、能源及建造界」分組裡勝出，晉身議員行列。在第一次開會之前，曾與當時任香港總督的彭定康打賭會在首次會議穿西裝出席。開會當日，彭定康遵守承諾，給了他一張有親筆簽名的500元鈔票。<br />\n<br />\n1998年與由陶君行、鄭家富、陳國樑等民主黨內議員組成的「少壯派」，爭取民主黨改革。<br />\n<br />\n1999年香港區議會選舉，競逐連任東區區議會樂康選區議席，敗於民建聯的陳達強。<br />\n<br />\n2000年香港立法會選舉，因堅持競逐立法會香港島選區議席，而退出民主黨。與陳添勝及陳國樑以獨立民主派身份，打出「窮人要出聲」的口號，組成一張名單參選，但最終落敗，未能重返立法會。<br />\n<br />\n2003年香港區議會選舉，在自己家居所在的東區樂康選區（範圍為柴灣康翠臺、樂翠臺、山翠苑），擊敗香港孔教學院院長湯恩佳之女兒湯棋淯，重返區議會。<br />\n<br />\n2004年香港立法會選舉中，曾健成以獨立候選人身分，夥拍香港職工會聯盟副主席鍾松輝及前香港大學學生會會長鄧徐中參選港島選區，最後仍然落選。<br />\n<br />\n2006年，曾健成分別籌組「SOS業主陣線」及「社會民主連線」。<br />\n<br />\n2007年香港區議會選舉，曾健成以1912票擊敗民建聯的黃家維，成功連任。<br />\n<br />\n2011年香港區議會選舉，競逐連任東區區議會樂康選區議席，以1871票對1916票，45票之差敗於報稱獨立的候選人李進秋。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%A5%E6%88%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2581%25A5%25E6%2588%2590&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBiVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=62d2071c\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9B%BE%E5%81%A5%E6%88%90</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:11:36.000Z","msg":"錯focus⋯⋯想問港督簽名喺錢度仲叫唔叫破壞公物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有特權<br />\n特赦自己"},{"pid":"22cc7e60c012331f4218701595ccee70807c5401","tid":1587593,"uid":63095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"262e228159049187c8e539c6a3d7b0d9c3553721","tid":1587593,"uid":294,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fc44625b2a2c13a68c46353e1cabc338bc9078ba","tid":1587593,"uid":322732,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:00:06.000Z","msg":"後生仔唔識阿牛好正常<br />\n唔經唔覺我都係大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"以前有咩威水史<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"簡單啲講姐係左膠或者大中華膠<br />\n<br />\n雖然已經大和解，都係咁話"},{"pid":"22c6755fb150e873567360db2dd6b966e36a4798","tid":1587593,"uid":34184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22cc7e60c012331f4218701595ccee70807c5401","tid":1587593,"uid":63095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"262e228159049187c8e539c6a3d7b0d9c3553721","tid":1587593,"uid":294,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fc44625